ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:44:24.000Z","msg":"敬老係敬呢啲老<br />\n唔係嗰班著數拎盡嘅老而不"},{"pid":"c134b57ca7cf467a08d8a24f07ad97df26ad5ed7","tid":144513,"uid":15851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:49:00.000Z","msg":"雖然幾多嘅勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62186c33f2eaabb8508bf8498f6e706b603bf7ae","tid":144513,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:55:54.000Z","msg":"其實比家人殺咗，扮成佢自己離家。"}]}